{"id":"5c938589-930e-4f7e-aefc-4ab0b48af9b7","name":"X-Men: Echoes of Evolution","description":"<p><em>You are a mutant whose powers emerged during an attack by a malevolent entity, revealing your unique mutant abilities. Taken in by Charles Xavier’s School for Gifted Youngsters, you meet a mix of teachers like Storm and Emma Frost, and students like Rogue, X-23, Jubilee, Kitty Pryde, and Jean Grey, and others— some immediately drawn to you while others remain skeptical.</em></p><p><em>As you learn to control your abilities and navigate budding relationships, global events challenge your powers and the bonds you’ve formed. In this school, your choices will shape not only your future but the fate of mutant kind.</em></p><p></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>The Professors:</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>Storm (Ororo Munroe):</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KlX1Rz5WdSrBlAlAq-z6N.webp\" style=\"width: 523px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>Emma Frost:</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vBuFCOaT45h1qS9pTiSEI.webp\" style=\"width: 529px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Students:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Rogue (Anna Marie):</em></strong></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/cHICB-iiOQblHrosPCZhd.webp\" style=\"width: 519px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: cen